org.sql: SELECT accounts.id FROM accounts INNER JOIN follows ON accounts.id = follows.account_id INNER JOIN users ON users.account_id = accounts.id WHERE follows.target_account_id = "$1" AND accounts.domain IS NULL AND users.current_sign_in_at > '2022-07-30 06:45:52.556433' ORDER BY accounts.id ASC LIMIT "$2"

rewrites.sql: SELECT accounts.id FROM accounts INNER JOIN follows ON accounts.id = follows.account_id WHERE follows.target_account_id = "$1" AND accounts.domain IS NULL ORDER BY accounts.id ASC LIMIT "$2"
